---
title: Portobello & Bell Pepper Fajita Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: Our chef-curated “perfect plates” are the answer to your dinner woes! This sizzling vegetarian spread stars portobello mushrooms, bell pepper, and buttery lime rice with tantalizing toppers: queso, fresh pico de gallo, sour cream, and lime wedges. Serve it all family style so everyone can build their own bowl!
